extends layout

block content
    section.page-header
        .container
            h1 About Us
            p.lead Empowering the next generation of drivers.

    section.company-background
        .container
            .background-grid
                .image
                    img(src="/images/hero.png", alt="Our History")
                .content
                    h2 Our Journey
                    p Founded in 2026, Exodus Motors started with a simple vision: to make premium automotive engineering accessible to those who value quality above all else. Over the months, we have grown into a global brand recognized for our commitment to excellence, sustainability, and customer satisfaction.
                    p Our team of experts works tirelessly to ensure that every car leaving our showroom meets the highest standards of safety and performance.

    section.mission-vision
        .container
            .mv-grid
                .mv-card
                    i.fas.fa-rocket
                    h3 Our Mission
                    p To provide innovative and sustainable automotive solutions that enhance the lives of our customers and protect our planet.
                .mv-card
                    i.fas.fa-eye
                    h3 Our Vision
                    p To be the world leader in luxury mobility, setting the standard for quality, design, and technological advancement.

    section.testimonials
        .container
            .section-header
                h2 What Our Clients Say
                .line
            .testimonial-grid
                .testimonial-card
                    p "The Exodus S-Class is by far the most comfortable car I've ever owned. The attention to detail is incredible."
                    .client-info
                        h4 John Doe
                        span CEO, TechVentures
                .testimonial-card
                    p "Exceptional service from start to finish. They truly care about their customers."
                    .client-info
                        h4 Jane Smith
                        span Architect
                .testimonial-card
                    p "Sustainability and performance finally meet in the E-Volt. It's the future of driving, available today."
                    .client-info
                        h4 Michael Chen
                        span Green Energy Consultant
                .testimonial-card
                    p "The buying process was seamless. I felt like a VIP from the moment I walked into the showroom."
                    .client-info
                        h4 Sarah Williams
                        span Fashion Designer
                .testimonial-card
                    p "Raw power combined with elegant design. Exodus Motors has created something truly special here."
                    .client-info
                        h4 David Miller
                        span Professional Driver
